title: Grating and Skeleton Key Puzzle
story: dungeo
author: Sharpee Team
description: Test the grating puzzle — locked/closed blocking, unlock with skeleton key, open, traverse both directions (ISSUE-053 regression)

---

# Setup: get lantern and skeleton key via GDT
> gdt
[OK: contains "GDT"]

> tk brass lantern
[OK: contains "Taken"]

> tk skeleton key
[OK: contains "Taken"]

# Teleport to the Clearing
> ah Clearing
[OK: contains "Teleported"]

> ex
[OK: contains "Returning"]

> switch on lantern
[OK: contains "on"]

> look
[OK: contains "Clearing"]

# Try going down through the locked grating — should be blocked
> down
[OK: contains "locked"]

# Teleport to the Grating Room to test from below
> gdt
[OK: contains "GDT"]

> ah Grating Room
[OK: contains "Teleported"]

> ex
[OK: contains "Returning"]

> look
[OK: contains "Grating Room"]

# Try going up through locked grating — should be blocked
> up
[OK: contains "locked"]

# Try opening the locked grating — should fail
> open grating
[OK: contains "locked"]

# Unlock the grating with the skeleton key
> unlock grating with skeleton key
[OK: contains "unlock"]

# Now open it
> open grating
[OK: contains "open"]

# Go up to the Clearing
> up
[OK: contains "Clearing"]

# Go back down to the Grating Room
> down
[OK: contains "Grating Room"]
